stories.title: Klusener, Kallis see SA through in rain-hit scramble
stories.summary: By his own standards, Lance Klusener has had a quiet time of it in the Standard Bank one-day series against New Zealand, but on Kingsmead on Wednesday night he showed that there's still a bit left in the great lump of wood he uses as a bat
